# Project data — media auto-ignored by extension globs above.
# Track metadata (json, md, yaml) and structure (.gitkeep). Archive contents
# fully ignored (heavy historical experiments) but the archive root stays
# present via .gitkeep so the directory survives a fresh clone.
projects/_archive/**
!projects/_archive/.gitkeep

work_log.md
*_work_log.md

# Exceptions — track test fixture assets under tests/fixtures/ even though *.png is globally ignored.
!tests/fixtures/
!tests/fixtures/**

# Exceptions — track golden screenshots under docs/design/golden/
!docs/design/golden/
!docs/design/golden/**

# Exception — Vite entry point. Without this the *.html global rule
# silently un-tracks index.html and CI fails with "Cannot resolve
# entry module index.html".
!frontend/index.html
